## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all dimensions of anti-science attitudes. The complexity of the issue means that some factors may be underrepresented or oversimplified. Additionally, the rapidly changing political and social landscape can influence the prevalence and nature of anti-science beliefs, which may not be fully captured in the current literature.